{"artefact":[["_response_info",{"status":"ok"}],["title","Approved driving instructor (ADI) fees"],["id","https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/approved-driving-instructor-adi-fees.json"],["web_url","https://www.gov.uk/approved-driving-instructor-adi-fees"],["format","answer"],["details",{"need_id":"B142","business_proposition":true,"alternative_title":"","overview":"Fees for taking the approved driving instructor (ADI) qualifying tests, and registering as an ADI with the Driving Standards Agency (DSA)","updated_at":"2012-10-08T17:05:47+00:00","body":"\n<div class=\"summary\">\n<p>Approved driving instructor (<abbr title=\"Approved driving instructor\">ADI</abbr>) test and registration fees are set by the Driving Standards Agency (<abbr title=\"Driving Standards Agency\">DSA</abbr>) - fees for driving instructor training vary and are set by training organisations.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2><abbr title=\"Approved driving instructor\">ADI</abbr> qualifying test fees</h2>\n\n<p>You have to pass the qualifying tests before you register as an <abbr title=\"Approved driving instructor\">ADI</abbr> with the <abbr title=\"Driving Standards Agency\">DSA</abbr>.</p>\n\n<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Fee type</th>\n      <th>Cost</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td><abbr title=\"Approved driving instructor\">ADI</abbr> theory test question book</td>\n      <td>\u00a36</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><abbr title=\"Approved driving instructor\">ADI</abbr> part 1 test</td>\n      <td>\u00a390</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><abbr title=\"Approved driving instructor\">ADI</abbr> part 2 test</td>\n      <td>\u00a3111</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><abbr title=\"Approved driving instructor\">ADI</abbr> part 3 test</td>\n      <td>\u00a3111</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>You have to pay the full amount again if you don\u2019t pass any of the tests, and want to take another one.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2><abbr title=\"Approved driving instructor\">ADI</abbr> registration and licence fees</h2>\n\n<p>You have to pay a fee to join the <abbr title=\"Approved driving instructor\">ADI</abbr> register, get a trainee licence and renew your registration every 4 years.</p>\n\n<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Fee type</th>\n      <th>Cost</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td>First <abbr title=\"Approved driving instructor\">ADI</abbr> certificate</td>\n      <td>\u00a3300</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Trainee driving instructor licence</td>\n      <td>\u00a3140</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Renewal or re-registration</td>\n      <td>\u00a3300</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Lost licence replacement</td>\n      <td>\u00a33</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>There are different <a href=\"http://www.dvtani.gov.uk/adi/fees.asp\" title=\"Fees for taking the ADI qualifying tests and registering\" rel=\"external\">fees for taking the <abbr title=\"Approved driving instructor\">ADI</abbr> qualifying tests and registering</a> in Northern Ireland.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Pass Plus instructor fees</h2>\n\n<p>You have to pay a fee to register as a Pass Plus instructor. You also have to pay for any refill packs you need.</p>\n\n<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Fee type</th>\n      <th>Cost</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Pass Plus starter pack</td>\n      <td>\u00a337</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Pass Plus refill pack</td>\n      <td>\u00a329</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<h2><abbr title=\"Driving Standards Agency\">DSA</abbr> special test fee</h2>\n\n<p>As an <abbr title=\"Approved driving instructor\">ADI</abbr>, you can take the <abbr title=\"Driving Standards Agency\">DSA</abbr> special test if you want your skills tested to the highest standard.</p>\n\n<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Fee type</th>\n      <th>Cost</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td><abbr title=\"Driving Standards Agency\">DSA</abbr> car special test</td>\n      <td>\u00a3144</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n"}],["tags",[{"title":"Business Link","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/tags/businesslink.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":null,"type":"legacy_source"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/with_tag.json?tag=businesslink","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/businesslink"},"parent":null},{"title":"Teaching people to drive","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/tags/driving%2Fteaching-people-to-drive.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Becoming an instructor, applying for licences, booking tests and rules","type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/with_tag.json?tag=driving%2Fteaching-people-to-drive","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/driving/teaching-people-to-drive"},"parent":{"title":"Driving","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/tags/driving.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Book your driving test or get a tax disc online, find out the legal requirements for buying, owning, importing or scrapping a car or motorcycle, and read about your rights and responsibilities as a driver.","type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/with_tag.json?tag=driving","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/driving"},"parent":null}}]],["related",[{"title":"Apply for your first approved driving instructor (ADI) badge","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/apply-first-approved-driving-instructor-adi-badge.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/apply-first-approved-driving-instructor-adi-badge","format":"transaction","details":{"need_id":"B127","business_proposition":true}},{"title":"Apply to become a driving instructor","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/a